The appletouch mouse devices are grabbed by the hid bus and not released even if apple driver says ENODEV (as expected).
Move the ignoration one level upper to deny the hid layer to grab the device and return error to the usb hid which, as a result, releases the device.
Otherwise input/mouse/appletouch and others needn't be attached.
